{"lastModified":1772813933826,"uri":"c::16875063630::vessel::d5cbfb71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia\n\nOneworld is a 31.5-meter (103-foot) luxury motor yacht, featuring expansive front, upper, and aft decks designed for all leisure and entertainment needs. Built with modern elegance by Gulf Craft, she is the perfect yacht for hosting intimate cruises, private parties, or corporate events, accommodating up to 100 guests. \n\nThe main deck offers a spacious, user-friendly area complete with a full-size bar and lounge space, ideal for entertaining guests. On the bow, relax in luxury with custom seating or soak up the sun on the sunbeds. Alternatively, enjoy the expansive sundeck with a jacuzzi, sunbeds, and a bar for added comfort. \n\nOneworld blends comfort and craftsmanship, with sophisticated interiors that highlight the yacht’s natural beauty. Large windows throughout the yacht provide exceptional light penetration, creating a bright and airy atmosphere on both the main deck and guest cabins. \n\nThe vessel boasts five elegant cabins for up to 12 guests, each with an en-suite bathroom. The main deck features a welcoming saloon where guests can relax and entertain in complete comfort. \n\nOneworld is the ultimate companion for your day on the water, offering luxury, style, and unforgettable experiences.","blueprint":{"name":"ONEWORLD","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f83be20-785a-11f0-9d56-79982d883a37/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f821070-785a-11f0-9d56-79982d883a37/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f8321e0-785a-11f0-9d56-79982d883a37/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f856bd0-785a-11f0-9d56-79982d883a37/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb71-